{"id":262885,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/明報-汕尾書記：刁官害農民變刁民/","date":"2012-11-13T21:17:05Z","modified":"2012-11-14T00:58:01Z","title":"明報 | 汕尾書記：刁官害農民變刁民","content":"<div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=javascript%3AclickSupport%28%29%3B\"><img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/shim.gif\" alt=\"推\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p>【明報專訊】在烏坎事件中大罵「境外媒體信得過，母豬都會上樹」而引起爭議的汕尾市委書記鄭雁雄，前日接受採訪時表示，拆遷時必須從觀念上尊重土地是農民的命根子，並且必須要在徵地補償中避免貪污腐敗。他說：「沒有天生的刁民，只有刁官，害得人家變成刁民。」 他又批評，基層村委會的人很容易誤認為「老子天下第一」，因而辦事不透明，以為沒人監督他們。</p>\n<p></p>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=javascript%3AclickSupport%28%29%3B\"><img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/shim.gif\" alt=\"推\" width=\"40\" height=\"25\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\">\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>相關文章 <img src=\"http://news.mingpao.com/image/b_round.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" /></p>\n</td>\n<td align=\"right\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20121114%2Fcaindex.htm\">[顯示全部題目]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2F20121114%2Fcaa1h.htm\">王岐山勢掌中紀委</a></li>\n<li>\n</li>\n<li